# Review AGENTS.md First

At the start of every new conversation, read and apply the instructions in `AGENTS.md` (project root) before responding to the user's request. Treat it as required context for all work in this project.

**Git:** Follow root `AGENTS.md` § **Git and version control** — no destructive git commands and no `git commit` / `git push` unless the user explicitly asks.
